BaseMetaManager (STATIC CLASS)
    ├── Manages ──> BaseMeta
BaseItem
    ├── Contains ──> BaseMeta
BaseFile (inherits BaseItem)
    ├── Extends ──> BaseMeta (size, comment, last_accessed_time)
BaseFolder (inherits BaseItem)
    ├── Extends ──> BaseMeta (file_count, file_names, folder_size)
BaseMeta
    ├── Contains ──> tagset
    ├── Contains ──> comment
    ├── Contains ──> file_count
